text.tspan: Lord I am Willing to Let You
Do not let me win today.
Duplicate Your heart in my heart,
Your love is the burning fire;
Things of my self You burn away.
Do gain in me what You desire—
A loving Bride to match You in every way.
Lord I open up for You to make
Your home in my heart li’l more today;
Make me a part of Your move
to build up Your church and bring the coming age.
